{
  "video_id": "BzeTjn0R2VY",
  "title": "What we can do about the culture of hate | Sally Kohn",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12951.0,
      "end_time": 15952.0,
      "text": "So people tell me I'm a nice person ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18200.0,
      "end_time": 22630.0,
      "text": "to the point where it's part of my personal and professional identity"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22870.0,
      "end_time": 26426.0,
      "text": "that I'm so nice and able to get along with anyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 26450.0,
      "end_time": 29683.0,
      "text": "even my most fierce opponents."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30837.0,
      "end_time": 33470.0,
      "text": "It's like my \"thing,\" it's what I'm known for."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 33710.0,
      "end_time": 36370.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 36610.0,
      "end_time": 38997.0,
      "text": "But what no one knows ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 41630.0,
      "end_time": 42586.0,
      "text": "is that I was a bully."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 44709.0,
      "end_time": 47121.0,
      "text": "Honestly, I didn't think about it much myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 47145.0,
      "end_time": 50623.0,
      "text": "I buried the memories for years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 50647.0,
      "end_time": 54179.0,
      "text": "and even still, a lot of it's really hazy."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 54203.0,
      "end_time": 56846.0,
      "text": "Denial, by the way, apparently is also one of my things."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 56870.0,
      "end_time": 58990.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58123.0,
      "end_time": 60678.0,
      "text": "But the more people started to praise me"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60703.0,
      "end_time": 63466.0,
      "text": "for being a liberal who could get along with conservatives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63490.0,
      "end_time": 65641.0,
      "text": "and the more I wrote articles about being nice"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65665.0,
      "end_time": 68689.0,
      "text": "and gave talks about being nice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68713.0,
      "end_time": 72868.0,
      "text": "the more I felt this hypocrisy creeping up inside me."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 74865.0,
      "end_time": 76690.0,
      "text": "What if I was actually really mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79877.0,
      "end_time": 82613.0,
      "text": "When I was 10 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 84155.0,
      "end_time": 87175.0,
      "text": "there was a girl in my class at school named Vicky."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 87199.0,
      "end_time": 88648.0,
      "text": "(Sigh)"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 88672.0,
      "end_time": 90218.0,
      "text": "And I tormented her ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 92330.0,
      "end_time": 93480.0,
      "text": "mercilessly."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 95359.0,
      "end_time": 96750.0,
      "text": "I mean, everyone did."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 96774.0,
      "end_time": 98358.0,
      "text": "Even the teachers picked on her."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 99769.0,
      "end_time": 101666.0,
      "text": "It doesn't make it any better, does it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 102975.0,
      "end_time": 106318.0,
      "text": "Vicky was clearly a troubled kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 106342.0,
      "end_time": 108884.0,
      "text": "She would hit herself and give herself bloody noses"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 108908.0,
      "end_time": 110425.0,
      "text": "and she had hygiene problems --"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 110449.0,
      "end_time": 112310.0,
      "text": "she had big hygiene problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 113193.0,
      "end_time": 115338.0,
      "text": "But instead of helping this girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 115362.0,
      "end_time": 118494.0,
      "text": "who was plainly suffering from hardships in her life ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 119889.0,
      "end_time": 121809.0,
      "text": "we called her \"Sticky Vicky.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 123821.0,
      "end_time": 125571.0,
      "text": "I called her \"Sticky Vicky.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 128633.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132993.0,
      "text": "My clearest memory is standing in the empty hallway"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 133170.0,
      "end_time": 134947.0,
      "text": "outside the fifth grade classrooms"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 134971.0,
      "end_time": 137771.0,
      "text": "waiting for Vicky to come out of the bathroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 137795.0,
      "end_time": 140986.0,
      "text": "and I have a clipboard and a pen and a survey I've made up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 141100.0,
      "end_time": 142775.0,
      "text": "asking about shampoo preferences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 142800.0,
      "end_time": 145915.0,
      "text": "like I'm doing a study for science class or something."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 145939.0,
      "end_time": 148340.0,
      "text": "And when Vicky comes out of the bathroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 148364.0,
      "end_time": 151174.0,
      "text": "I pounce on her and I ask her what shampoo she uses."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 151198.0,
      "end_time": 153404.0,
      "text": "Now, to put this in perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 153428.0,
      "end_time": 155471.0,
      "text": "I can't remember the names of my teachers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 155495.0,
      "end_time": 158512.0,
      "text": "I can't remember the names of any of the books I read that year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158536.0,
      "end_time": 161108.0,
      "text": "I pretty much can't remember anything from fifth grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 161132.0,
      "end_time": 164790.0,
      "text": "but I remember that Vicky told me she used White Rain shampoo."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 165285.0,
      "end_time": 166466.0,
      "text": "Clear as yesterday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 166490.0,
      "end_time": 167640.0,
      "text": "like it just happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 168775.0,
      "end_time": 169925.0,
      "text": "And as classes let out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 169949.0,
      "end_time": 172728.0,
      "text": "I ran down the hall shouting at all the other kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 172752.0,
      "end_time": 175109.0,
      "text": "\"Sticky Vicky uses White Rain shampoo."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 175133.0,
      "end_time": 177400.0,
      "text": "Don't use White Rain shampoo"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 177280.0,
      "end_time": 180185.0,
      "text": "or you'll smell like Sticky Vicky.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 182641.0,
      "end_time": 184642.0,
      "text": "I forgot about this memory for a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 184666.0,
      "end_time": 186506.0,
      "text": "When I finally started remembering it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 186530.0,
      "end_time": 188151.0,
      "text": "I immediately needed to know more."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 188175.0,
      "end_time": 190667.0,
      "text": "I reached out to friends and eventually social media,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 190691.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "and I did everything I could to try to find Vicky."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 193500.0,
      "end_time": 195852.0,
      "text": "I needed to know that she was OK,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 195876.0,
      "end_time": 197546.0,
      "text": "and that I hadn't ruined her life."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 199471.0,
      "end_time": 200510.0,
      "text": "(Sigh)"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 200534.0,
      "end_time": 202540.0,
      "text": "But what I quickly realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 202780.0,
      "end_time": 205300.0,
      "text": "was I wasn't just trying to figure out what happened to Vicky."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 205369.0,
      "end_time": 207656.0,
      "text": "I was trying to figure out what happened to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 209802.0,
      "end_time": 211960.0,
      "text": "When I was 10 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 211120.0,
      "end_time": 215889.0,
      "text": "I treated another human being like some worthless other ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 216820.0,
      "end_time": 218296.0,
      "text": "like I was better than her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 219349.0,
      "end_time": 220567.0,
      "text": "and she was garbage."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 222760.0,
      "end_time": 223906.0,
      "text": "What kind of a nice person does that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 224578.0,
      "end_time": 226189.0,
      "text": "I mean, I know I was only a kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 226213.0,
      "end_time": 227695.0,
      "text": "but not all kids do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 227719.0,
      "end_time": 229968.0,
      "text": "Most kids don't do that, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 231168.0,
      "end_time": 233537.0,
      "text": "So, what if I wasn't nice after all?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 233561.0,
      "end_time": 236378.0,
      "text": "I was really just a hateful monster."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 237914.0,
      "end_time": 242805.0,
      "text": "Then I started to notice myself having these mean impulses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 242830.0,
      "end_time": 244676.0,
      "text": "thinking mean thoughts"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 244700.0,
      "end_time": 245916.0,
      "text": "and wanting to say them."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 251195.0,
      "text": "Admittedly, most of my mean thoughts were about conservatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 251219.0,
      "end_time": 256900.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 256329.99999999997,
      "end_time": 257360.99999999997,
      "text": "But not just conservatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 257385.0,
      "end_time": 261486.0,
      "text": "I also caught myself thinking mean things about mushy, centrist liberals"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 261510.0,
      "end_time": 263388.0,
      "text": "and greedy Wall Street bankers"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 263412.0,
      "end_time": 264870.0,
      "text": "and Islamophobes"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 264894.0,
      "end_time": 266368.0,
      "text": "and slow drivers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 266392.0,
      "end_time": 268677.0,
      "text": "because I really hate slow drivers."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 268701.0,
      "end_time": 271220.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 271244.0,
      "end_time": 274244.0,
      "text": "And as I'd catch myself in these moments of hypocrisy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 274268.0,
      "end_time": 277967.0,
      "text": "either I was just noticing them or they were getting worse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 277991.0,
      "end_time": 279574.0,
      "text": "especially in the last few years."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 280149.0,
      "end_time": 282274.0,
      "text": "And as I felt more hateful --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 282298.0,
      "end_time": 284586.0,
      "text": "rageful, really --"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 284610.0,
      "end_time": 287850.0,
      "text": "I noticed the world around me seemed to be getting more hateful, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 287874.0,
      "end_time": 290428.0,
      "text": "Like there was this steady undercurrent of hate"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 290452.0,
      "end_time": 292557.0,
      "text": "bubbling up all around us"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 292581.0,
      "end_time": 294288.0,
      "text": "and increasingly overflowing."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 295973.0,
      "end_time": 298461.0,
      "text": "So the plus side, I guess,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 298485.0,
      "end_time": 303703.0,
      "text": "is that I realized that hate was not just my problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 303727.0,
      "end_time": 306822.0,
      "text": "which is like, the most selfish plus side ever --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 306846.0,
      "end_time": 308373.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 308813.0,
      "end_time": 314329.0,
      "text": "because now instead of just my own hate and cruelty to try to figure out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 314353.0,
      "end_time": 318334.0,
      "text": "I had a whole world of hate I wanted to unravel"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 318358.0,
      "end_time": 320413.0,
      "text": "and understand and fix."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 322506.0,
      "end_time": 327482.0,
      "text": "So I did what all overly intellectual people do when they have a problem"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 327507.0,
      "end_time": 329540.0,
      "text": "that they want to understand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 329780.0,
      "end_time": 330229.0,
      "text": "and I wrote a book."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 330253.0,
      "end_time": 332433.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 333260.0,
      "end_time": 334919.0,
      "text": "I wrote a book about hate."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 335407.0,
      "end_time": 336556.0,
      "text": "Spoiler alert:"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 337443.0,
      "end_time": 338594.0,
      "text": "I'm against it."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 338618.0,
      "end_time": 341395.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 341419.0,
      "end_time": 344100.0,
      "text": "Now at this point, you might be thinking to yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 344250.0,
      "end_time": 345825.0,
      "text": "\"Why are y'all worried about hate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 345849.0,
      "end_time": 347000.0,
      "text": "You didn't hate Vicky."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 347240.0,
      "end_time": 348800.0,
      "text": "Bullying isn't hate.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 350474.0,
      "end_time": 351623.0,
      "text": "Isn't it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 353267.0,
      "end_time": 354576.0,
      "text": "Gordon Allport,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 354600.0,
      "end_time": 358822.0,
      "text": "the psychologist who pioneered the study of hate in the early 1900s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 358846.0,
      "end_time": 361339.0,
      "text": "developed what he called a \"scale of prejudice.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 361363.0,
      "end_time": 367850.0,
      "text": "At one end are things like genocide and other bias-motivated violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 367109.0,
      "end_time": 368640.0,
      "text": "But at the other end"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 368665.0,
      "end_time": 371830.0,
      "text": "are things like believing that your in-group"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 371854.0,
      "end_time": 375450.0,
      "text": "is inherently superior to some out-group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 375474.0,
      "end_time": 380236.0,
      "text": "or avoiding social interaction with those others."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 381583.0,
      "end_time": 382789.0,
      "text": "Isn't that all hate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 384186.0,
      "end_time": 385996.0,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't an accident"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 386210.0,
      "end_time": 389187.0,
      "text": "that I was a rich kid picking on a poor kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 390982.0,
      "end_time": 395212.0,
      "text": "or that Vicky, it turns out, would eventually end up being gay."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 396861.0,
      "end_time": 400954.0,
      "text": "Poor kids and gay kids are more likely to be bullied,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 400978.0,
      "end_time": 404263.0,
      "text": "even by kids who also end up being gay."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 405988.0,
      "end_time": 408894.0,
      "text": "I know there was a lot going on in my little 10-year-old mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 408918.0,
      "end_time": 411586.0,
      "text": "I'm not saying hate was the only reason I picked on Vicky"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 411610.0,
      "end_time": 414584.0,
      "text": "or even that I was consciously hateful or anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 414608.0,
      "end_time": 416436.0,
      "text": "but the fact is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 416460.0,
      "end_time": 421405.0,
      "text": "the people we discriminate against in our public policies and in our culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 421429.0,
      "end_time": 426800.0,
      "text": "are also the groups of people most likely to be bullied in school."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 427984.0,
      "end_time": 429666.0,
      "text": "That is not just a coincidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 431799.0,
      "end_time": 433190.0,
      "text": "That's hate."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 435554.0,
      "end_time": 437924.0,
      "text": "I am defining hate in a broad way"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 439451.0,
      "end_time": 442340.0,
      "text": "because I think we have a big problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 443214.0,
      "end_time": 446873.0,
      "text": "And we need to solve all of it, not just the most extremes."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 446897.0,
      "end_time": 448147.0,
      "text": "So for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 448172.0,
      "end_time": 450736.0,
      "text": "we probably all agree that marching down the street,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 450760.0,
      "end_time": 454380.0,
      "text": "chanting about you should take away rights from some group of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 454620.0,
      "end_time": 456112.0,
      "text": "because of their skin color or their gender,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 456136.0,
      "end_time": 458850.0,
      "text": "we'd all agree that's hate, right? OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 459594.0,
      "end_time": 463387.0,
      "text": "What if you believe that group of people is inferior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 464771.0,
      "end_time": 465981.0,
      "text": "but you don't say it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 467546.0,
      "end_time": 468695.0,
      "text": "Is that hate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 469780.0,
      "end_time": 473400.0,
      "text": "Or what if you believe that group of people is inferior"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 473424.0,
      "end_time": 475693.0,
      "text": "but you aren't aware that you believe it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 475718.0,
      "end_time": 477304.0,
      "text": "what's known as implicit bias."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 477990.0,
      "end_time": 479140.0,
      "text": "Is that hate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 479918.0,
      "end_time": 482157.0,
      "text": "I mean they all have the same roots, don't they?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 482181.0,
      "end_time": 485195.0,
      "text": "In the historic patterns of racism and sexism"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 485219.0,
      "end_time": 488303.0,
      "text": "that have shaped our history and still infect our society today."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 488327.0,
      "end_time": 489808.0,
      "text": "Isn't it all hate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 490573.0,
      "end_time": 493660.0,
      "text": "I'm not saying they're the same thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 493900.0,
      "end_time": 495416.0,
      "text": "just like I am not saying"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 495440.0,
      "end_time": 498194.0,
      "text": "that being a bully is as bad as being a Nazi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 498218.0,
      "end_time": 502162.0,
      "text": "just like I'm not saying that being a Nazi is the same thing as punching a Nazi ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 502636.0,
      "end_time": 508335.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 508359.0,
      "end_time": 512352.0,
      "text": "But hating a Nazi is still hate, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 513294.0,
      "end_time": 516100.0,
      "text": "What about hating someone who isn't as enlightened as you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 517231.0,
      "end_time": 519302.0,
      "text": "See, what I learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 520533.0,
      "end_time": 523730.0,
      "text": "is that we all are against hate"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 523970.0,
      "end_time": 525103.0,
      "text": "and we all think hate is a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 525929.0,
      "end_time": 527668.0,
      "text": "We think it's their problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 528550.0,
      "end_time": 529992.0,
      "text": "not our problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 530824.0,
      "end_time": 532126.0,
      "text": "They're hateful."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 532690.0,
      "end_time": 535219.0,
      "text": "I mean, if I think the people who didn't vote like me"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 535243.0,
      "end_time": 538720.0,
      "text": "are stupid racist monsters who don't deserve to call themselves Americans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 538744.0,
      "end_time": 540423.0,
      "text": "alright, fine, I'm not being nice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 540447.0,
      "end_time": 541694.0,
      "text": "I get it."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 541718.0,
      "end_time": 543115.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 543139.0,
      "end_time": 546409.0,
      "text": "I'm not hateful, I'm just right, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 546433.0,
      "end_time": 548116.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 548140.0,
      "end_time": 549290.0,
      "text": "Wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 551346.0,
      "end_time": 553695.0,
      "text": "We all hate."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 554568.0,
      "end_time": 558818.0,
      "text": "And I do not mean that in some abstract, generic sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 558842.0,
      "end_time": 561430.0,
      "text": "I mean all of us ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 562571.0,
      "end_time": 564111.0,
      "text": "me and you."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 565684.0,
      "end_time": 570929.0,
      "text": "That sanctimonious pedestal of superiority on which we all place ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 570953.0,
      "end_time": 574280.0,
      "text": "that they are hateful and we are not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 574304.0,
      "end_time": 578178.0,
      "text": "is a manifestation of the essential root of hate:"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 578202.0,
      "end_time": 581731.0,
      "text": "that we are fundamentally good and they are not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 583106.0,
      "end_time": 584695.0,
      "text": "which is what needs to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 585968.0,
      "end_time": 589724.0,
      "text": "So in trying to understand and solve hate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 589749.0,
      "end_time": 592667.0,
      "text": "I read every book and every research study I could find,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 592691.0,
      "end_time": 596857.0,
      "text": "but I also went and talked to some former Nazis"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 596881.0,
      "end_time": 598390.0,
      "text": "and some former terrorists"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 598414.0,
      "end_time": 601260.0,
      "text": "and some former genocidal killers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 601500.0,
      "end_time": 605233.0,
      "text": "because I figured if they could figure out how to escape hate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 605258.0,
      "end_time": 606688.0,
      "text": "surely the rest of us could."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 607617.0,
      "end_time": 611804.0,
      "text": "Let me give you just one example of the former terrorist I spent time with"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 611828.0,
      "end_time": 613760.0,
      "text": "in the West Bank."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 613719.0,
      "end_time": 616569.0,
      "text": "When Bassam Aramin was 16 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 617692.0,
      "end_time": 622170.0,
      "text": "he tried to blow up an Israeli military convoy with a grenade."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 623828.0,
      "end_time": 626202.0,
      "text": "He failed, fortunately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 626226.0,
      "end_time": 628656.0,
      "text": "but he was still sentenced to seven years in prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 628680.0,
      "end_time": 631617.0,
      "text": "When he was in prison, they showed a film about the Holocaust."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 631641.0,
      "end_time": 632791.0,
      "text": "Up until that point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 632816.0,
      "end_time": 635685.0,
      "text": "Bassam had thought the Holocaust was mostly a myth."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 635709.0,
      "end_time": 637508.0,
      "text": "He went to go watch the film"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 637533.0,
      "end_time": 640619.0,
      "text": "because he thought he would enjoy seeing Jews get killed."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 642424.0,
      "end_time": 646187.0,
      "text": "But when he saw what really happened, he broke down crying."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 647691.0,
      "end_time": 649117.0,
      "text": "And eventually, after prison,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 649141.0,
      "end_time": 652502.0,
      "text": "Bassam went on to get a master's degree in Holocaust studies"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 652526.0,
      "end_time": 656556.0,
      "text": "and he founded an organization where former Palestinian combatants"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 656581.0,
      "end_time": 658962.0,
      "text": "and Israeli combatants come together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 659963.0,
      "end_time": 662622.0,
      "text": "work together, try to find common ground."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 664287.0,
      "end_time": 667779.0,
      "text": "By his own account, Bassam used to hate Israelis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 669304.0,
      "end_time": 672456.0,
      "text": "but through knowing Israelis and learning their stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 672480.0,
      "end_time": 674265.0,
      "text": "and working together for peace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 674289.0,
      "end_time": 675550.0,
      "text": "he overcame his hate."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 677654.0,
      "end_time": 681189.0,
      "text": "Bassam says he still doesn't hate Israelis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 682183.0,
      "end_time": 683952.0,
      "text": "even after the Israeli military --"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 685232.0,
      "end_time": 687617.0,
      "text": "shot and killed his [10]-year-old daughter, Abir,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 687642.0,
      "end_time": 689342.0,
      "text": "while she was walking to school."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 692210.0,
      "end_time": 694270.0,
      "text": "(Sigh)"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 694339.0,
      "end_time": 697102.0,
      "text": "Bassam even forgave the soldier who killed his daughter."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 698339.0,
      "end_time": 700100.0,
      "text": "That soldier, he taught me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 701998.0,
      "end_time": 706220.0,
      "text": "was just a product of the same hateful system as he was."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 711515.0,
      "end_time": 713727.0,
      "text": "If a former terrorist ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 716169.0,
      "end_time": 720423.0,
      "text": "if a terrorist can learn to stop hating"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 720447.0,
      "end_time": 722591.0,
      "text": "and still not hate when their child is killed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 722615.0,
      "end_time": 726621.0,
      "text": "surely the rest of us can stop our habits"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 726645.0,
      "end_time": 729255.0,
      "text": "of demeaning and dehumanizing each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 729279.0,
      "end_time": 732613.0,
      "text": "And I will tell you there are stories like Bassam's all over the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 732637.0,
      "end_time": 734598.0,
      "text": "plus study after study after study"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 734622.0,
      "end_time": 739741.0,
      "text": "that says, no, we are neither designed nor destined as human beings to hate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 739765.0,
      "end_time": 743385.0,
      "text": "but rather taught to hate by the world around us."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 743409.0,
      "end_time": 744584.0,
      "text": "I promise you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 744608.0,
      "end_time": 748102.0,
      "text": "none of us pops out of the womb hating black people or Republicans."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 748126.0,
      "end_time": 753150.0,
      "text": "There is nothing in our DNA that makes us hate Muslims or Mexicans."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 753513.0,
      "end_time": 754715.0,
      "text": "For better or for worse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 754739.0,
      "end_time": 758291.0,
      "text": "we are all a product of the culture around us."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 759870.0,
      "end_time": 761919.0,
      "text": "And the good news is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 761943.0,
      "end_time": 764687.0,
      "text": "we're also the ones who shape that culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 766139.0,
      "end_time": 767731.0,
      "text": "which means we can change it."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 768661.0,
      "end_time": 774600.0,
      "text": "The first step is starting to recognize the hate inside ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 774850.0,
      "end_time": 775694.0,
      "text": "We need to catch ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 775718.0,
      "end_time": 778199.0,
      "text": "and our hateful thoughts in all their forms"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 778224.0,
      "end_time": 779987.0,
      "text": "in all of us ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 781556.0,
      "end_time": 783924.0,
      "text": "and work to challenge our ideas and assumptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 783948.0,
      "end_time": 785394.0,
      "text": "That doesn't happen overnight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 785418.0,
      "end_time": 786773.0,
      "text": "I am telling you right here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 786797.0,
      "end_time": 789701.0,
      "text": "it is a lifelong journey, but it's one we all need to take."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 790367.0,
      "end_time": 791541.0,
      "text": "And then second:"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 791566.0,
      "end_time": 794947.0,
      "text": "if we want to challenge the hate in our societies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 794971.0,
      "end_time": 798916.0,
      "text": "we need to promote policies and institutions and practices"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 798940.0,
      "end_time": 801669.0,
      "text": "that connect us as communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 802295.0,
      "end_time": 805365.0,
      "text": "Literally, like integrated neighborhoods and schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 805389.0,
      "end_time": 807867.0,
      "text": "That by the way is the reason to support integration."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 807891.0,
      "end_time": 810144.0,
      "text": "Not just because it's the right thing to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 810168.0,
      "end_time": 813593.0,
      "text": "but because integration systematically combats hate."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 813617.0,
      "end_time": 815950.0,
      "text": "There are studies that teenagers who participate"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 815975.0,
      "end_time": 820162.0,
      "text": "in racially integrated classes and activities reduce their racial bias."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 820186.0,
      "end_time": 823556.0,
      "text": "And when little kids go to racially integrated kindergartens"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 823580.0,
      "end_time": 825700.0,
      "text": "and elementary schools --"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 825724.0,
      "end_time": 827525.0,
      "text": "they develop less bias to begin with."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 828672.0,
      "end_time": 832593.0,
      "text": "But the fact is in so many ways and in so many places around our world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 832617.0,
      "end_time": 835387.0,
      "text": "we are separated from each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 836740.0,
      "end_time": 838972.0,
      "text": "In the United States, for instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 838996.0,
      "end_time": 843439.0,
      "text": "three-quarters of white people don't have any non-white friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 844683.0,
      "end_time": 848753.0,
      "text": "So in addition to promoting those proactive solutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 848777.0,
      "end_time": 852603.0,
      "text": "the other thing we need to do is upend the hate in our institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 852627.0,
      "end_time": 854630.0,
      "text": "and our policies"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 854870.0,
      "end_time": 858826.0,
      "text": "that perpetuate dehumanization and difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 858850.0,
      "end_time": 860778.0,
      "text": "and otherizing and hate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 860802.0,
      "end_time": 866541.0,
      "text": "like systems of sexual harassment and sexual assault in the workplace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 866565.0,
      "end_time": 870730.0,
      "text": "or our deeply racially imbalanced"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 870754.0,
      "end_time": 874125.0,
      "text": "and deeply racially biased criminal \"justice\" system."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 874814.0,
      "end_time": 876469.0,
      "text": "We need to change that."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 876494.0,
      "end_time": 878360.0,
      "text": "Again, it will not happen overnight."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 878384.0,
      "end_time": 880334.0,
      "text": "It needs to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 881763.0,
      "end_time": 882913.0,
      "text": "And then ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 884123.0,
      "end_time": 885615.0,
      "text": "when we connect together"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 886885.0,
      "end_time": 889607.0,
      "text": "in these connection spaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 890518.0,
      "end_time": 893319.0,
      "text": "facilitated by connection systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 894591.0,
      "end_time": 897374.0,
      "text": "we need to change the way we talk to each other"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 898992.0,
      "end_time": 900469.0,
      "text": "and connect with one another"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 900494.0,
      "end_time": 905843.0,
      "text": "and relate with generosity and open-mindedness"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 905867.0,
      "end_time": 907271.0,
      "text": "and kindness and compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 907296.0,
      "end_time": 908479.0,
      "text": "and not hate."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 909837.0,
      "end_time": 911252.0,
      "text": "And that's it."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 911276.0,
      "end_time": 912426.0,
      "text": "That's it."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 912451.0,
      "end_time": 916713.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 916737.0,
      "end_time": 918832.0,
      "text": "I have solved it all, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 918856.0,
      "end_time": 920700.0,
      "text": "That's it."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 920310.0,
      "end_time": 921189.0,
      "text": "That is pretty much --"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 921214.0,
      "end_time": 922381.0,
      "text": "there's a few details --"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 922405.0,
      "end_time": 924358.0,
      "text": "but that's pretty much all we have to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 924383.0,
      "end_time": 926106.0,
      "text": "It's not that complicated, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 927556.0,
      "end_time": 928843.0,
      "text": "But it's hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 930279.0,
      "end_time": 934739.0,
      "text": "The hate that we feel towards certain groups of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 935814.0,
      "end_time": 938661.0,
      "text": "because of who they are or what they believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 938686.0,
      "end_time": 942980.0,
      "text": "is so ingrained in our minds and in our society"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 942122.0,
      "end_time": 943661.0,
      "text": "that it can feel inevitable"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 945310.0,
      "end_time": 946477.0,
      "text": "and impossible to change."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 949393.0,
      "end_time": 950677.0,
      "text": "Change is possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 953148.0,
      "end_time": 957735.0,
      "text": "Just look at the terrorist who became a peace activist."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 959483.0,
      "end_time": 964515.0,
      "text": "Or look at the bully who learned to apologize to her victim."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 967338.0,
      "end_time": 972490.0,
      "text": "The entire time I was traveling around the Middle East and Rwanda"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 972514.0,
      "end_time": 973897.0,
      "text": "and across the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 973921.0,
      "end_time": 978600.0,
      "text": "hearing these unbelievable stories of people in communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 978300.0,
      "end_time": 980713.0,
      "text": "who had left entire histories of hate behind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 980737.0,
      "end_time": 982194.0,
      "text": "I was still looking for Vicky."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 983240.0,
      "end_time": 985810.0,
      "text": "It was so hard find her that I hired a private investigator"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 985834.0,
      "end_time": 987271.0,
      "text": "and he found her."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 987296.0,
      "end_time": 989194.0,
      "text": "I mean, he sort of found her."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 989218.0,
      "end_time": 993522.0,
      "text": "The truth is, it became clear that the person I'm calling Vicky"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 993547.0,
      "end_time": 998339.0,
      "text": "had gone to extraordinary lengths to hide her identity."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 1000560.0,
      "end_time": 1004425.0,
      "text": "But anyway, a year after I began my journey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 1006560.0,
      "end_time": 1008524.0,
      "text": "I wrote Vicky an apology."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 1010200.0,
      "end_time": 1011461.0,
      "text": "And a few months later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 1012600.0,
      "end_time": 1013750.0,
      "text": "she wrote back."
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 1014670.0,
      "end_time": 1016733.0,
      "text": "(Sigh)"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 1017900.0,
      "end_time": 1018958.0,
      "text": "I'm not going to lie,"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 1018980.0,
      "end_time": 1020682.0,
      "text": "I wanted to be forgiven."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 1025180.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1026168.0000000001,
      "text": "I wasn't."
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 1026190.0,
      "end_time": 1027340.0,
      "text": "(Sigh)"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 1027810.0,
      "end_time": 1030739.0,
      "text": "She offered me sort of conditional forgiveness."
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 1030770.0,
      "end_time": 1032212.0,
      "text": "What she wrote was ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 1033160.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1037827.0000000001,
      "text": "\"Messages such as yours cannot absolve you of your past actions."
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 1038910.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1042253.0000000001,
      "text": "The only way to do that is to improve the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 1042280.0,
      "end_time": 1044595.0,
      "text": "prevent others from behaving in similar ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 1046930.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1047602.0000000001,
      "text": "and foster compassion.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 330,
      "start_time": 1049880.0,
      "end_time": 1051402.0,
      "text": "And Vicky's right."
    },
    {
      "index": 331,
      "start_time": 1053530.0,
      "end_time": 1054880.0,
      "text": "Which is why I'm here."
    },
    {
      "index": 332,
      "start_time": 1055600.0,
      "end_time": 1056751.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 333,
      "start_time": 1056780.0,
      "end_time": 1063780.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}